description.en: Launchblock, the decentralized Launch Pad which provides all users with the ecosystem to access early stage projects whilst maximizing the benefits of decentralized finance (De-Fi). Decreasing expense and providing significant opportunity, Launchblock is the one-stop-shop for all projects launching and users accessing a Launch Pad.
